info.author: ENOT LLC
info.description:
ENOT Lite is an inference framework with unified interface for running inference on different types
of execution providers (TensorRT, OpenVINO).
Additionally, this framework provides presets which are easy to use and can help finding
an optimal configuration for inference.

To use this package please refer to our [documentation page](https://enot-lite.rtd.enot.ai/en/stable/).

Visit [our website](https://enot.ai) for more information.
